data.description: One-time opportunity for this gorgeous two-story home, well located in charming Chapman Heights Community. Featuring 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, a large family room with a fireplace, a kitchen with an island, a butler and walk-in pantry, a spacious laundry room and an extra storage room. Added features include ceiling fan in all bedrooms, window shutters, recessed lighting, low maintenance backyard presenting a refreshing view of the golf course and mountains, plus a covered Alumawood patio. The 3-car garage adds convenience with epoxy flooring. Located in the Yucaipa/Calimesa Unified School and near city amenities, shopping, restaurants. Come and experience the comfort, elegance, and natural beauty this home offers.
